{
  "$comment": "Stack → skill mapping for `ad init --skills-mode smart`. Resolution: global = union(always, stacks[s].global) − union(stacks[s].exclude). project = union(stacks[s].project). Only skills that exist in the repo are listed here — keep in sync with skills/ folder. New always-block skills (skill-author, session-close, gepa-evolve-inline) are added as they ship.",
